# =============================================================================
# JCPR Trading System — Environment Template
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values:
#     cp .env.example .env
#     chmod 600 .env
#
# Then edit .env with your real credentials.
#
# CRITICAL SECURITY NOTES:
#   1. NEVER commit .env to git (it's in .gitignore).
#   2. .env file MUST have permissions 0600 (owner read/write only).
#      The loader will REFUSE to read .env if perms are looser.
#   3. NEVER share .env via Slack, email, or any chat tool.
#   4. If a secret is leaked, immediately revoke at KIS Developers portal:
#      https://apiportal.koreainvestment.com/
#
# Get your KIS API keys at:
#   https://apiportal.koreainvestment.com/howto-service
# =============================================================================

